<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><image-reference id="_10e3e2f6-cae6-47e6-ad4f-1bad87938074"><num>9.2.3a</num><title id="_a2f8ddeb-43c3-4b1a-832c-e90f7aaddbf3">Typical construction of external walls</title><image alt="Typical construction of external walls" height="1504" heightdpi="200" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/9-2-3a-typical-construction-of-external-walls.svg" width="1200" widthdpi="200"><image height="1504" heightdpi="200" href="C:\Users\bkiem\AppData\Roaming\Quark\XML Author\Temp\media1_15f7c5d1-eb30-477b-bb56-1dd4e5c1a9f1.jpg" width="1200" widthdpi="200"/></image><desc-note id="_ce4493e1-6848-4922-b01b-920ffa7317e5"><ol outputclass="numbered"><li id="_0697879a-6bb2-4f2a-960d-60d3a7946a38">The <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_83407c74-6381-4705-9322-6f50fab1ccf2" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">external wall</xref> is deemed to extend to the underside of <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1377_5.9.0.xml#_be8a1d10-4119-4eb0-a014-07a806b104ff" id="_d472780c-bd0d-434f-8153-9a018a598a28" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-combustible</xref> roof covering, or <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1377_5.9.0.xml#_be8a1d10-4119-4eb0-a014-07a806b104ff" id="_113c92c5-a3b0-43a4-87df-ddda8e294a6d" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-combustible</xref> eaves lining, when constructed as shown.</li><li id="_9ab25d57-3121-4d9f-9b6a-0440768b2043">Where sarking is installed it must be located so that ponding of water is avoided between the fascia and the first roofing batten.</li><li id="_4